{"tid":984533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【派吉儀】藍利是襯白花　電訊商被嘲　網民︰差粒糖","createTime":"2019-01-17T01:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T01:38:55.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41ef583ef3ca092af85b543aeec942929138cf56","tid":984533,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:21:27.000Z","msg":"<strong>藍利是襯白花　電訊商被嘲派吉儀　網民︰差粒糖</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117081525126-0117_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fbkn-20190117081525126-0117_00822_001.html&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6f3826e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/bkn-20190117081525126-0117_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190117/photo/bkn-20190117081525126-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190117081823\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190117081525126-0117_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190117081823&h=2cbafafa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個設計都幾特別&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"eb5337159e460363ee6eef2954cc3b603b3cefa0","tid":984533,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:21:34.000Z","msg":"派利是當然想利利是是，有個好意頭。惟近日有電訊商派發的利是封，以藍底配上白花，收到的市民當堂嚇一跳，直呼︰「大吉你個利是」。<br />\n<br />\n從相片可見，長方形的利是封以紫藍色作底色，右邊襯以銀白色燙金的白花。發貼者批評該利是封與殯儀物品的用色極為相似︰「邊個設計利是封嘅企出嚟，我保證唔打死你。新年流流死人藍襯白花，畀啲長輩見到肯定即時同你開年」。<br />\n<br />\n有別於傳統大紅大金的的設計隨即引起網民的議論︰「係咪因為佢本身嘅logo係藍色」、「差粒糖同紙巾」、「吉儀利是不用分得那麼細」；有人則認為並無不妥︰「藍色有咩問題，幾靚呀」、「咩年代呀？黑色都有人用啦」、「我個人重視內涵多啲」。<br />\n<br />\n《港呢啲》已向該電訊公司查詢事件，正候回覆。"},{"pid":"5cabcd4accf54aad79e247169923f9355b61be16","tid":984533,"uid":139967,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"其實幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c9c478c332d14c11b5543e7e880af4863a2f8f","tid":984533,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5cabcd4accf54aad79e247169923f9355b61be16","tid":984533,"uid":139967,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"其實幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"agree"}]}